```plantuml
@startuml doitintl_banias

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Frontend>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<Backend>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<ExternalService>> LightGray
}

component "Frontend" <<Frontend>> {
  [HTTP API] as API
  [Event Validator] as Validator
  [Event Publisher] as Publisher
  [Metrics Exporter] as Metrics
}

component "Backend" <<Backend>> {
  [Dataflow Pipeline] as Pipeline
  [Schema Manager] as SchemaManager
}

cloud "Google Cloud Platform" {
  [Pub/Sub] <<ExternalService>>
  [BigQuery] <<ExternalService>>
  [Cloud Storage] <<ExternalService>>
}

[Prometheus] <<ExternalService>>
[Stackdriver] <<ExternalService>>

API --> Validator : Receives events
Validator --> Publisher : Validates and batches
Publisher --> [Pub/Sub] : Publishes events

Pipeline --> [Pub/Sub] : Reads events
Pipeline --> [BigQuery] : Writes events
SchemaManager --> [Cloud Storage] : Loads schemas
Pipeline ..> SchemaManager : Uses

Metrics --> [Prometheus] : Exposes metrics
Metrics --> [Stackdriver] : Integrates with

note right of API : /track endpoint
note right of Metrics : /metrics endpoint
note bottom of Publisher : Async publishing\nusing goroutines
note bottom of Pipeline : Dynamic table writing
note bottom of SchemaManager : Supports schema evolution

@enduml
```